Week_5 
Date- (24/2/2025 – 2/3/2025)

HARDWARE AND SOFTWARE REQUIREMENTS

1. HARDWARE REQUIREMENTS

• Processor:  Intel Core i5 or above 
• RAM:  Minimum 4 GB required 
• Storage:  Minimum 512 GB SSD/HDD 
• Internet:  Good internet connectivity

2. SOFTWARE REQUIREMENTS

• Operating System:  Windows/Linux/MacOS 
• Programming Languages:  Solidity, Javascript, Typescript, Tailwind,CSS 
• Libraries:  CryptoJs, Web3.js, OpenZeppelin 
• Blockchain Platform:  Metamask 
• Backend:  Node.js

